cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL 

The paper proposes a method for few-shot learning using convolutional neural networks and relation networks. This topic falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG), with a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper discusses attention mechanisms, which are commonly used in natural language processing (cs.CL).
